{"tid":1420871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"討論一下大埔10號遊行","createTime":"2019-08-06T06:06:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T04:21:24.000Z","uid":243158,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ad6c5868be9c32bfd72c90f5b0cb96f934a0feca","tid":1420871,"uid":243158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:06:13.000Z","msg":"其實經過琴日 大家都睇到大部分大埔人無咩裝備 亦都無咩經驗 最重要係 佢地無勇武既心<br />\n同時 和理非又唔敢出黎 見到有催淚彈又亂咁跑 仲要有人唔帶口罩眼罩 著住短衫短褲行上前 <br />\n所以如果其他區既手足諗住10號入黎大埔既話 真係要有定心理準備 大埔人未必會咁主動上前線 可能真係要你地主動叫佢地出黎 振奮一下大埔人 <br />\n另外 大埔人都傾緊可能遊行完就去機場或者其他區幫手 所以前線既手足真係要有哂共識 確保有足夠既哨兵同人手先好決定衝定唔衝 <br />\n千其唔好將其他區既模式放落大埔<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b8cec707adf52073947c7470f9619541e78b08","tid":1420871,"uid":243158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:06:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e17452b698e2a73a17cf698c01d3bcbd5f73b1a","tid":1420871,"uid":243158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:06:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed83ed4b69c50cb1d9613d65b072b7fe3ac4d34e","tid":1420871,"uid":243158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:06:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48a0a53ba3ee97f3b930e3b4e4f131b0a149ebbc","tid":1420871,"uid":243158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:07:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b3631586a8082bd2faa2dcbc8856c4be209d0bd","tid":1420871,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:08:51.000Z","msg":"民建聯大埔支部：<br />\n<br />\n新界大埔寶鄉街112號二樓<br />\n2638 1144<br />\n2638 2244<br />\ndabtaipo@dab.org.hk<br />\ndabtaipo@dab.org.hk<br />\n<br />\n昌運辦事處<br />\n 大埔昌運中心商場二樓119B號舖<br />\n2663 2238<br />\n2663 2183<br />\ndabtaipo@dab.org.hk<br />\ndabtaipo@dab.org.hk<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n太和聯絡處<br />\n 大埔太和邨麗和樓121號地下<br />\n2650 3886<br />\n2653 2533<br />\ndabtaipo@dab.org.hk<br />\ndabtaipo@dab.org.hk"},{"pid":"5fad1026ae23b59257d1d697c7f37